{"tid":918361,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有潔癖點樣kiss同做愛","createTime":"2018-11-27T07:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T01:46:00.000Z","uid":58609,"like":4,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"fd9173f9e8e8468192a7710f5044d40c7536d96b","tid":918361,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"背景:我有輕度潔癖,就算屋企人既口水尾都接受唔到<br />\n<br />\n琴日第一次同女友做,<br />\n我係處佢唔係所以全程佢lead住我<br />\n當佢主動濕吻時,我只係覺得口水好噁心<br />\n點撚解要用條脷打轉又啜黎啜去<br />\n當佢瀨我全身時,好爽但D口水漬真係頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n之後到我serve佢時,<br />\n話曬睇左咁多年AV,學到唔少,<br />\n全身漫遊搵佢敏感點都一路好順利<br />\n但當瀨佢食到D汗既咸味,<br />\n又開始覺得嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最難頂係我瀨到西時,<br />\nD分泌好難頂,我好努力咁瀨但洞口真心瀨唔落,太多分泌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同時身體上既口水開始乾,開始有口水臭味,聞到即冇feel<br />\n<br />\n然後.....就冇然後啦,我硬唔起了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇潔癖既巴絲講下,到底點克服潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f2eb53fd8e8197a444f45ba26ed22c2fcc541b","tid":918361,"uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"喺個口度"},{"pid":"a15b0638c36b72d448727fadf399ed6a5387469c","tid":918361,"uid":65256,"like":101,"dislike":4,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:05:30.000Z","msg":"公然上連登鬧自己條女臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0241e0f7d07357777a3a9018256bb4ab52153e21","tid":918361,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"消毒酒精"},{"pid":"e578c92cdc700c5b58a69930d8fe90416cbce8aa","tid":918361,"uid":121393,"like":54,"dislike":3,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"去奶一個比其他男人屌過嘅閪<img src=\"/asse